author: The Babylon Bee
description:
These parents just want to let their little one learn basic shapes and colors, but he's about to get a lesson in standing up to patriarchal power structures through expressions of gender non-conformity. Not good.

Family entertainment should be entertainment! Meet Mech West, the new all-ages action-adventure series about kids and robots in the Old West. Watch it right on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@mechwestshow
title: Trying To Find A Show Your Kids Can Watch In 2025
